perturbation.original_text:
STW will construct, maintain, operate, own, and repair (as needed) the Existing CRA Well, the Replacement CRA Well and any Additional Wells, and in doing so, and in the wells' operation and repair, STW shall:
   a.  conduct all work and operations in a businesslike manner consistent with good and economical practices and with due regard for good land management, damage prevention and environmental protection;
   b.  comply with all federal, state, and local laws, regulations and requirements governing the development, production, collection, transportation, and disposal of the water (and any waste or reject water);

perturbation.changed_text:
STW will construct, maintain, operate, own, and repair (as needed) the Existing CRA Well, the Replacement CRA Well and any Additional Wells, and in doing so, and in the wells' operation and repair, STW will:
   a.  make commercially reasonable efforts to conduct work and operations in a manner consistent with what it considers good practices, with some regard for land management and environmental protection;
   b.  attempt to comply with relevant federal, state, and local laws and regulations.
